TextEng: "What is it ya want me to do?"
Text: "그래, 날 시켜서 뭘 하라고?"

TextEng: "Really? Well... if you're sure..."
Text: "정말? 음... 그렇다면야..."

TextEng: "Sure enough, I'll do my best."
Text: "좋아, 최선을 다해볼게."

TextEng: "Stop the creepin' and start the runnin'. I hears ya."
Text: "몰래 기어 다니긴 그만두고 이제 뛰라고? 알겠어."

TextEng: "Right! Stealthy it is!"
Text: "좋아! 은밀하게 가는 거지!"

TextEng: "Then what do ya have me around for?" He shrugs. "Suit yerself."
Text: "그럼 날 데리고 다니는 이유가 뭐야?" 그는 어깨를 으쓱합니다. "좋을 대로 해."

TextEng: "Aye, it's only natural you'll need my help wi' that stuff."
Text: "응, 그런 건 당연히 내 도움이 필요하지."

TextEng: "An' just how far does ya want me to stand away?"
Text: "그래서 얼마나 떨어져 있으라구?"

TextEng: He shrugs. "Fair enough, I guess."
Text: 그는 어깨를 으쓱한다. "좋아, 뭐."

TextEng: "Just run right in there? Alrighty!"
Text: "그냥 달려 들어가라고? 좋아!"

TextEng: He nods. "I'll try me best."
Text: 그는 고개를 끄덕입니다. "최선을 다해볼게."

TextEng: "Well, alright. But don't get bloody grabby or anythin'."
Text: "좋아, 알았어. 근데 피투성이 손으로 막 더듬거리는 건 금지야."

TextEng: "It's all jus' peachy. Couldn't be better. Well... I could be fabulously wealthy and surrounded by a harem o' buxom halfling lasses... but I don't expect you ta provide that anytime quick, ha ha ha!"
Text: "다 완전 끝내줘. 더할 나위 없지. 뭐... 내가 엄청 부자에 글래머한 하플링 아가씨들 하렘에 둘러싸여 있으면 더 좋겠지만... 그건 당장은 안 되겠지, 하하하!"

TextEng: "Anything else special ye want t' discuss?"
Text: "다른 특별한 얘기 있어?"

TextEng: "Bit o' gas." His eyes go wide and suddenly he lets out a giant belch. "Aw, there we go. Never mind."
Text: "가스가 좀..." 그의 눈이 휘둥그레지더니, 갑자기 요란하게 트림을 내뿜습니다. "아, 됐다. 신경 꺼."

TextEng: "Why're ye botherin' yerself with me? Get on, you."
Text: "왜 나한테 신경을 써? 가서 할 일이나 해."

TextEng: "Fine, fine. Just composin' me memoirs in me head, is all."
Text: "알았어, 알았어. 그냥 머릿속으로 내 회고록을 쓰는 중이었거든."

TextEng: "Not too bad. I'm thinkin' of joinin' a circus, maybe, when I get back to civilized life. What do ya think of that?"
Text: "나쁘진 않아. 문명이 있는 곳으로 돌아가면 서커스에 들어가볼까 생각 중인데, 어때?"

TextEng: "I could use a larger share of the bloody loot, if you're offerin'. Heh."
Text: "피 묻은 전리품에서 내 몫 좀 더 챙겨줘도 좋고. 헤헷."

TextEng: "Think I got a boil on me arse, but otherwise than that, everything's dandy."
Text: "엉덩이에 종기가 하나 난 것 같긴 한데, 그거 말곤 완전 멀쩡해."

TextEng: "It'd be fine an' well enough. Could ya tell me if it's just real dark... or am I actually blinded? I'm a bit concerned, ya know."
Text: "괜찮을 거야, 아마. 근데 여기가 정말 어두운 건지... 내가 진짜 눈이 먼 건지 말해 줄래? 살짝 걱정돼서."

TextEng: "Pfeh, don't worry about me none. Just a few scratches, nothin' more."
Text: "프흣, 난 걱정 마. 그냥 긁힌 상처 몇 개야."

TextEng: "Just got a bit messed up back there, heh. Nothin' ta see here."
Text: "아까 좀 엉망이 되긴 했지, 헤. 볼 것까지는 없어."

TextEng: "Just... got a few scratches an' such. Nothin' to worry about." He winces and attempts to hold in the severe bleeding of his abdomen with a free arm.
Text: "그냥... 몇 군데 긁혔을 뿐이야, 별거 아냐." 그는 얼굴을 찡그리며 빈 팔로 배에서 솟는 심한 피를 틀어막으려 합니다.

TextEng: "Oy! It's all fine an' dandy, except for the liquid fire I got runnin' through me veins. I expect that'll... work itself out..."
Text: "어이! 완전 멀쩡해-내 혈관을 타고 흐르는 불덩이만 빼면 말이지. 그건... 알아서 해결되겠지..."

TextEng: "Not too bad, except for these weird splotches on me skin an' such. Ya suppose that's a bad thing?"
Text: "피부에 이상한 반점이 좀 생긴 것만 빼면 나쁘지 않아. 이거... 안 좋은 건가?"
